text: Spartaco Cesaretti (born 19 January 1921) is a Sammarinese former sports shooter. He competed in the 50 metre pistol event at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1921 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Sammarinese male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of San Marino Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics
